Subject: Re: [T2] broken tranny mount- options?

76-79 will work. Be careful, older ones look very similar. Compare to
your broken one to make sure it's the same. The main difference will
be in the thickness of the bellhousing. If I recall, the 76-79 091
bellohousing is about 3/4 of an inch thicker.


-David


